About Event

​We're teaming up to kick off the next YC batch (W26) with an epic party and have reserved the entire Standard Deviant Brewing Pier 70.

​So before hunkering down for the batch, come enjoy some great food and drinks (beer, wine, cider, and NA) and exchange war stories with fellow YC founders. Alumni are welcome!
